text: "Wishful Sinful" is a 1969 song by The Doors and is the fourth single from their fourth studio album The Soft Parade. It went to number 44 in the United States and number 3 in Denmark. == References == Category:1969 songs Category:1960s ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:The Doors songs Category:Chamber rock songs Category:Baroque pop songs
